name: InfoPath Analyzer
tagline: The source code of InfoPath Analyzer
body:
### What's InfoPath Analyzer?
It's a tool to show the inside of InfoPath templates. It allows you to search fields, list tree hierarchy across views and etc. 

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with InfoPath Analyzer? File an issue on [GitHub](https://github.com/mazong1123/infopathanalyzer/issues).
